### Course Overview  
I completed the **Crash Course on Python** by Google on Coursera. This course was designed to teach Python from scratch ‚Äî no prior programming experience needed ‚Äî while focusing on automation and real-world scripting applications. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}  

It‚Äôs part of Google‚Äôs *IT Automation with Python* Professional Certificate, giving it real relevance for technical operations, system administration, and security roles. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}  

